struct Y1 {  \n   initonly  \n   static int staticConst1;  \n  \n   initonly  \n   static int staticConst2 = 0;  \n  \n   static Y1() {  \n      staticConst1 = 0;  \n   }  \n};  \n```  \n  \n## See Also  \n [Classes and Structs](../windows/classes-and-structs-cpp-component-extensions.md)"}